Implement a complete "Text Tools" module for phung.work.
## Goal
Build a modern collection of browser-based text utilities.
Requirements:
- Everything runs completely client-side.
- No backend.
- No API calls.
- No user data leaves the browser.
- Mobile responsive.
- Dark mode compatible.
- Fast (<50ms for common operations).
- Able to handle very large text (up to 5MB) without freezing.
- Follow the existing UI/UX style of phung.work.
- Reuse shared components whenever possible.
- Do not modify existing architecture unless necessary.
GENERAL REQUIREMENTS
Each tool should include:
- Page title
- Description
- Input textarea
- Output textarea
- Live processing when appropriate
- Copy button
- Clear button
- Swap button (when applicable)
- Download result (.txt)
- Upload text file (.txt)
- Character statistics
- Processing time
- Keyboard shortcuts
- Mobile optimized layout
